{"parse":{"title":"Stonescale Eel","pageid":35489,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{tooltip\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||10}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_11\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=13422\n|ilvl=45\n|name=Stonescale Eel}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Stonescale Eel''' is obtained by [[fishing]] and is a component in [[Stonescale Oil]] (made with [[Alchemy]]). The eels and their alchemic products are used in high-level [[potions]] used by [[raid]]ers, [[Craftsman's Writs|Craftsman's Writ]] quests for [[Argent Dawn]] reputation, and a [[Tier 0.5]] armor set quest. As a result, stonescale eel is one of the most lucrative fish one can catch.\n\n\n== Source ==\n'''Stonescale Eels''' are [[Nocturnal]] so the best time to catch them is between the hours of 12 am and 6 am. They require a minimum skill in fishing of around 180 + lures.  The best place to catch eels is any deep water location in [[Azshara]], the most popular being Scalebeard's Cave and by Duke Hydraxis.  Expect around 10% drop rate when fishing.  A higher rate can be obtained from around the cave in the bay, but this requires a minimum fishing skill of 235 just to be allowed to fish there.  At this skill level, though, most of the fish will \"get away\". Schools of stonescale eels appear off the main coast of Azshara during the night hours (during the day the spawn points are usually filled with firefin snappers and oily blackmouth).\n\n== Stonescale Eel as an Ingredient ==\nStonescale Eel is used in the following [[Alchemy|alchemic]] recipe:\n*{{item|icon=|Stonescale Oil}}\n\n== Stonescale Eel as a Quest Objective ==\n*{{questlong|Neutral|60|Craftsman's Writ - Stonescale Eel}} (requires 40)\n\n== Notes ==\nAs of [[Patch 1.11]] there are Swarms of Stonescale Eels that function much like schools of other valuable fish. They can be found along coastlines in [[Feralas]], [[Tanaris]], [[Azshara]] and southern [[Stranglethorn Vale]].  The [[Argent Dawn]] is also gaining several quests for the eels, both directly and crafted into items, so demand should stay steady or even increase.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13422}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/stonescale_eel.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:Eels]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft alchemy ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common quest items]]\n[[Category:Alchemy Materials]]"}}}